"data\";s:35:\"WPGlobus Multilingual Notices 2.3.0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-multilingual-notices/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 03 Feb 2021 00:00:55 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Plugin Updates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpglobus.com/?p=17054\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:582:\"<p>2021-02-02 - version 2.3.0 * (Cookie Notice) Added filter for the `blogname` option on `cookie-notice-welcome` page. 2020-11-25 - version 2.2.0 * Updated plugin names. * Moved up the tab on the WPGlobus Options page. \"Multilingual Notices\" adds multilingual capabilities to the plugins displaying GDPR/cookies notifications. Click here to download!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-multilingual-notices/\">WPGlobus Multilingual Notices 2.3.0</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Gregory Karpinsky\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:726:\"<p>2021-02-02 &#8211; version 2.3.0<br />\n* (Cookie Notice) Added filter for the `blogname` option on `cookie-notice-welcome` page.</p>\n<p>2020-11-25 &#8211; version 2.2.0<br />\n* Updated plugin names.<br />\n* Moved up the tab on the WPGlobus Options page.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&#8220;Multilingual Notices&#8221; adds multilingual capabilities to the plugins displaying GDPR/cookies notifications.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpglobus.com/product/wpglobus-multilingual-notices/\">Click here to download!</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-multilingual-notices/\">WPGlobus Multilingual Notices 2.3.0</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"WPGlobus 2.6.3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 30 Jan 2021 00:00:22 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Plugin Updates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpglobus.com/?p=11724\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:331:\"<p>Version 2.6.3</p>\n<p>(Vendor/Yoast) Fixed issue with empty Open Graph description.<br />\n 	(Updater) Missing assets in the ZIP file.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-update/\">WPGlobus 2.6.3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Alex G.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1565:\"<h3>WPGlobus Version 2 is a new major version, designed to work with WordPress 5.</h3>\n<p>It is compatible with the Gutenberg Editor, which is now a part of the WordPress Core.</p>\n<p><em>Note: the Classic Editor plugin v.1.0 is not compatible with WordPress 4! For WordPress 4.9 and earlier versions, please stay with the Classic Editor v.0.5</em></p>\n<p><strong>2021-01-30 &#8211; version 2.6.3</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>(Vendor/Yoast) Fixed issue with empty Open Graph description.</li>\n<li>(Updater) Missing assets in the ZIP file.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2021-01-27 &#8211; version 2.6.2</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>(Core) Added <code>wpglobus_show_title_fields</code> filter.</li>\n<li>(Core/Post Types) Added the <code>Ultimate Member</code> plugin post types to the <code>\"hidden types\"</code> list.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Thank you for your continuing support! Please enjoy the new release and do not hesitate to contact us should you have any questions.</h3>\n<h3>FYI: Please read <a href=\"https://wpglobus.com/faq/when-i-save-one-language-everything-published-in-the-other-language-disappears/\">FAQ</a></h3>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/WPGlobus/WPGlobus/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">The complete history of changes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpglobus/\">Download Free WPGlobus Multilingual WordPress Plugin!</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-update/\">WPGlobus 2.6.3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"WPGlobus for Ultimate Member 1.1.0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-for-ultimate-member/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 19:30:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Plugin Updates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpglobus.com/?p=24097\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\