</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Alex G.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1361:\"<h2>The recent updates</h2>\n<h2>2020-12-12 &#8211; version 4.2.0</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>WC tested up to: 4.8.0</li>\n<li>ADDED:\n<ul>\n<li>A link to the &#8220;Translate WooCommerce Taxonomies&#8221; page with filter from <code>Attributes</code> tab.</li>\n<li>Info message about in-place edit multilingual attributes to <code>Attributes</code> tab.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>UPDATED:\n<ul>\n<li>Export to Excel.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2020-11-24 &#8211; version 4.1.0</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>FIXED:\n<ul>\n<li>Header for the multilingual <code>Product short description</code> metabox.</li>\n<li><code>Cannot read property \'top\' of undefined</code> the on <code>About WPGlobus WC Translations</code> page.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li>Subscribe to the <a href=\"https://wpglobus.com/product/woocommerce-wpglobus/\">WPGlobus extension for WooCommerce</a> upgrades and support!</li>\n<li>Read the <a href=\"https://wpglobus.com/extensions/woocommerce-wpglobus/woocommerce-wpglobus-changelog/\">complete history of changes</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/woocommerce-wpglobus-update-%f0%9f%8c%90/\">WPGlobus for WooCommerce 4.2.0</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_expli